OL,3,CCardiff City fans demand 'urgent'
OL,4,Cmeeting with club's owner after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,FCardiff City Supporters' Trust have
OL,8,Fdemanded an urgent meeting with the
OL,9,Fclub's owner Vincent Tan after they
OL,10,Fwere relegated from the Championship
OL,11,Fon Saturday.
OL,13,FThe side's 0-0 draw against West
OL,14,FBromwich Albion at Cardiff City
OL,15,FStadium saw them relegated to the
OL,16,Fthird division of English football for
OL,17,Fthe first time in 22 years.
