OL,3,CCardiff City fans demand 'urgent'
OL,4,Cmeeting with club's owner after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,FIn a statement, the trust said: "Big
OL,8,Fchanges are needed, and needed now, to
OL,9,Favoid a further downward spiral in the
OL,10,Ffortunes of the club that we fans
OL,11,Flove."
OL,13,FThe stalemate at Cardiff City Stadium
OL,14,Fleft the Bluebirds, playing their
OL,15,Fsecond match since sacking Omer Riza
OL,16,Fand putting Aaron Ramsey in interim
OL,17,Fcharge, at the foot of the table.
OL,19,FIn its statement, the trust blasted
OL,20,Fthe running of the club over the last
OL,21,Ffew years.
