OL,3,CCardiff City fans demand 'urgent'
OL,4,Cmeeting with club's owner after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,FIt said: "We are dedicated fans of
OL,8,FCardiff City FC, some of us have
OL,9,Fsupported the club through thick and
OL,10,Fthin for more than 60 years. However,
OL,11,Fwe could not let the dreadful
OL,12,Frelegation to League One after more
OL,13,Fthan 20 years in higher divisions go
OL,14,Fwithout comment.
OL,16,F"Relegation has been coming since the
OL,17,F2021-22 season and the failure to
OL,18,Faddress fundamental required changes
OL,19,Ffrom the top down has now come home to
OL,20,Froost.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G3/16
