OL,7,F"As the season has progressed and it
OL,8,Fquickly became evident that things
OL,9,Fwere not going to plan on the pitch,
OL,10,Fit has been far from clear who on the
OL,11,Fclub board, if anyone, has been
OL,12,Fadvising the owner on footballing
OL,13,Fmatters. If any such advice and
OL,14,Frecommendations have in fact been
OL,15,Fgiven, it is unclear if any notice has
OL,16,Fbeen taken of such advice and
OL,17,Frecommendations.
