OL,7,FThe trust is calling for the
OL,8,Fappointment of a club board member
OL,9,Fwith specialist football knowledge and
OL,10,Fexperience, while dub the appointment
OL,11,Fof Omer Riza a "mistake... when there
OL,12,Fmany experienced managers available to
OL,13,Frecruit", and call for an experienced
OL,14,Fmanager for the League One campaign
OL,15,Fnext season.
