OL,7,F"Continuing the failings of the past
OL,8,Fthat have led to us celebrating our
OL,9,F125th anniversary with a relegation
OL,10,Fare not going to turn around our
OL,11,Ffortunes on the pitch. Big changes are
OL,12,Fneeded, and needed now, to avoid a
OL,13,Ffurther downward spiral in the
OL,14,Ffortunes of the club that we fans
OL,15,Flove."
